name: Annual Congress on Gynecology and Womens Healthcare
content: Gynecology Congress 2019 welcomes attendees, presenters, and exhibitors from all over the world for the “Annual Congress on Gynecology and Women’s Healthcare” which is going to be held during December 4-5, 2019 Dubai, UAE. Hurry! Register your slot now!! Avail Early Bird Offer Submit your Abstract Mail to: gynecology@pulsusglobal.com Event website: https://gynaecology.pulsusconference.com Abstract Submission link: https://gynaecology.pulsusconference.com/abstract-submission Registration page link: https://gynaecology.pulsusconference.com/registration Scientific sessions: https://gynaecology.pulsusconference.com/call-for-abstracts Brochure: https://gynaecology.pulsusconference.com/conference-brochure WhatsApp number: +44-1828-270013
